{"type": "article", "id": 14181, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-08-31T08:04:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 15196, "name": "厨房用具"}, {"id": 11882, "name": "播放器"}, {"id": 15197, "name": "收纳包"}, {"id": 34, "name": "自行车"}, {"id": 811, "name": "家居"}, {"id": 10372, "name": "应用程序"}, {"id": 862, "name": "设计师"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606002919pNhF1jQbCAw8XEnG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tM-Cuisine Collection by Joseph Joseph\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>伦敦厨具品牌 Joseph Joseph 认为，微波炉除了加热以外，其实还有很多功能被人无视了，而一项重要的原因是加热用具的缺失，于是最近他们推出了一系列微波炉专用器具，但是其目的却是希望能够提供用餐的全套需求，而不仅仅是加热食物。这套产品全部采用注射成型聚丙烯材料，使得微波炉使用安全健康，它包括为米饭、谷物、意面、鸡蛋准备的不同的容器，这些东西通常不是微波炉制作，但是有了合适的容器，他们也可以为用餐带来一些惊喜。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141819hgdFmlf35s2UYBTC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141820hW5AIlGPi3eJ9Rks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002859yow0ROVLi84YJ5tI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002859PUgxijF8mrlJ0ZEX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002900EZdi21b7yHIcheLk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73290598\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002900rXcjIJMip2x6SHOt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85683761\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141820PGvH2zFSdRZJNjkn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141820w57IUqtMD6PvcSr8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141821e78lDusR3tAPGOr6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141822RW9pTYwH1q5Kudts.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64316239\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141822khUwyKdo9LsvVbYF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141822rAJCD4aIXZ0sjhwn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tRadio Activity by Installations And Interaction\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是来自 Installations And Interaction 工作室的一位设计师 Gemma Roper 推出的一个“音乐猎手”，它是一个互联网启用流装置，效果是让用户可以根据节奏选择音乐，当它接收到节奏信号，会自动从音乐库里面选取相应节奏的乐曲开始播放。播放器强调艺术上的随机性，所以不设置播放记录和播放引导，界面中央像是一个节拍器，可以通过向上向下的滑动改变乐曲的节奏。此外，播放器外观设计十分简洁时尚，<a href=\"http://www.gemmaroper.com/RADIO-ACTIVITY\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看更多信息，<a href=\"http://www.gemmaroper.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以看 Gemma Roper 的更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002900OGomdPJtLeNWrIFf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002901Y7vmk98fyOt5Cjr2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55867971\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002901op0Muf3hPlSbdq1E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002902kKHxRi8n3cFjXzal.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002902mOtxAaGWQhrTSP91.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060029033p6kP5xeaRE7InKl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tTech Dopp Kit by This Is Ground\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是来自洛杉矶的 This Is Ground 推出的一个便当盒子式的极简收纳包，可以把各种线材整齐地摆放在里面，同时，耳机、电源、适配器等也有专门的区域可以收纳，中间设计了一个小的拉链包收容易丢失的小物品。目前有乳白色和棕色两种颜色可以选择，售价 199 美元，这是<a href=\"http://thisisground.com/collections/organizers/products/tech-dopp-kit?variant=4318219589\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002903mhixT7Oaj1kHDfec.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002903TWQ49iLrHgCxKYDA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002904xH5g8dZ9aNlcTer6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002905PfMr1uZnx3CGWz8F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002905kSD3VeNjH7FPoRAb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002905jhSzt08Teq7LBG1R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002906ibLrh2R8TZ5B0FKe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t#UnchainMe by Martone Cycling Co &amp; Ron Robinson \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Martone Cycling 公司和零售品牌 Ron Robinson 共同推出了一系列充满艺术气息的自行车，他们邀请了许多艺术家来为自行车设计外观色彩，包括来自洛杉矶的 ToMo，Fallen Fruit，Sket One 以及 Zachary Crane。这些自行车有的呈现彩虹的颜色，有的像是融化的巧克力，有的则遍布绽放的花朵。这些车目前正在 Santa Monica 展出，同时也出售（当然价格不菲），<a href=\"http://martonecycling.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002906zXQJPvqc8HMNnpWL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002907pC95rjkQo1fxymZA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002907ERs8mezInOtTy6Lv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002908TL4PU3emZwDuyKpn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060029091CocFOE7aRgdPZjB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002909GZbmo7O3fLycYaVt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tWinter Collection by Melanie Abrantes\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是来自加州的设计师 Melanie Abrantes 推出的一个家居饰品系列，包括花盆、餐具、花瓶、收纳盒等等，设计师擅长使用软木和皮革为设计作品带来温暖和优雅的气质，这套作品名为“Winter Collection”，也意味着用作品的质感为寒冷的冬天带来一份家的温暖。<a href=\"http://www.melanieabrantes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看设计师的更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002909wj0qYr6HcvROoFhg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002910sRldhk5ubHI6wnpz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002910H0l98WpUQCEORzX2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63645833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002911uAOiQZ8pwxszdeNW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002911XqcvQE6dZ7uOez2B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002912OAZEBhrW2Rb4FHaV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002912L8YprDoizWca34vE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060029135mIC023OeZJyBD8S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002913kr1ex5OaKRPW4GES.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060029141gL03av2KDCZYlsR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002914iYflPF5XMyO78Jwz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002915grQpqWJKkGbmI7e1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002915mUlyAtQJ84ifn2pV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002916gIPnfz37EJN1Cyhx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tAstropad by Astro HQ \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Astro HQ 最近推出了一个可以将 iPad 的屏幕映射到 Mac 上的程序 Astropad。它在为 iPad 提供高质量镜像的同时，集成了 Wacom 的 Creative Stylus，Adonit 的 Jot Touch 和 Jaja Hex3 配合 Mac 使用。用户随时可以用手指或压敏手写笔记录灵感，然后通过 Astropad For Mac 的两种不同的模式绘制（Draw）和移动缩放（Move &amp; Zoom）自己的设计方案。新技术的使用使得反应速度更快，笔触也更加流畅。<a href=\"http://astropad.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002916qXYlSCUZLusmFGOP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002917RDmFTCwKt9iekVdu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002917VKcSgbpxDWFdkIqZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50855746\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002917LaP5xMGHX2sB7OFu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58924205\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002918I7rtYBRKqzPh6fZ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70537897\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002918CtjNo1vRzWlLnMGB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}